
########################################
# Unreal Engine 5 / C++ Project GitIgnore
########################################

# ===== Generated binaries =====
Binaries/
Build/
DerivedDataCache/
Intermediate/
Saved/

# ===== Project user settings =====
# 本地开发者特定的配置文件，不需要提交
*.uproject.user
*.uproject.userprefs
*.suo
*.user
*.useropts
*.xcodeproj
*.xcworkspace
*.xcuserdata/
*.vs/

# ===== IDE & Editor settings =====
.vs
.vscode/
.idea/
.vsconfig
.claude
.opencode

# ===== Logs & temporary files =====
*.log
*.log.*
*.tmp
*.bak
*.swp

# ===== Crash dumps =====
crashdumps/

# ===== Config files that are machine-specific (optional) =====
# 注意: 如果团队协作，需要保留 Default*.ini 配置
# 可以按团队约定选择性忽略
# Config/DefaultEditor.ini
# Config/DefaultGame.ini
# Config/DefaultInput.ini

# ===== Packaging & build artifacts =====
# 打包生成文件和可执行文件不需要提交
*.apk
*.app
*.exe
*.dmg
*.ipa
*.pdb
*.lib
*.dll
*.a
*.appx
*.appxbundle

# ===== Node modules for plugins/tools =====
node_modules/

# ===== Ignore hidden system files =====
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ===== Fab Assets =====
#Content/FreeAnimationsPack
#Content/GameAnimationSample
Content/ThirdPerson
